Description.zhCN:
生产建筑
莫比斯地面机械部队生产设施。

开启：
- 狱焰骑士
- 使重型武装工程车可以建造莫比斯舰队空港
- 使重型武装工程车可以建造莫比斯高级军备站
Description.enUS:
Production Building
Moebius Ground Machinery Force production facility.

Enable:
- Hellfire Knight
- Use< c val="#ColorAttackInfo">Heavy Armed Engineering Vehicle can build Moebius Fleet Airport
- use Heavy Armed Engineering Vehicle can build Moebius Advanced Armament Station

Tooltip.zhCN:
莫比斯高速战车。能够变为空中单位。可以使用隐形技能。

可以对地和对空。
Tooltip.enUS:
Moebius High Speed ​​Chariot. Can be transformed into an air unit. Can use stealth skills.

Can be used against ground and air.

Tooltip.zhCN:
莫比斯快速歼击战车。闲置时充能武器攻击单一目标造成大量伤害。可以使用磁力鱼叉和磁电过载技能。

可以对地。
Tooltip.enUS:
Moebius fast destroyer tank. When idle, the charged weapon attacks a single target, causing massive damage. Can use the Magnetic Harpoon and Magneto-Electric Overload skills.

Can target the ground.

Tooltip.zhCN:
莫比斯高速反轻甲战车，对一条直线上的敌方单位造成范围伤害。能够变形为近距离战斗机甲。可以使用后燃推进、车体过载和引擎熔毁技能。

可以对地。
Tooltip.enUS:
Moebius is a high-speed anti-light armor tank that causes area damage to enemy units in a straight line. Able to transform into a close combat mecha. Can use afterburning propulsion, hull overload and engine meltdown skills.

Can target the ground.
Sends constructed units to the designated point. Workers rallied to resources will begin gathering automatically.
Tooltip.ruRU: Отправляет созданные войска в указанную точку. Рабочие, отправленные на месторождение минералов или веспена, автоматически начнут добычу ресурсов.

Tooltip.zhCN: 将建筑变形为移动速度缓慢的空中单位以便重新部署。建筑在着陆前无法生产单位、研发升级或使用技能。
Tooltip.enUS: Transform buildings into slow-moving air units for redeployment. Buildings cannot produce units, develop upgrades, or use skills until they land.
Halts construction of this structure. The partial construction will remain.
Tooltip.ruRU: Приостановить сооружение этого строения. Впоследствии его можно будет продолжить.

Tooltip.enUS: Drops the current order without performing it, and allows you to select a different order.
Tooltip.ruRU: Отменить текущий приказ и отдать следующий.

Tooltip.enUS: Drops the current order without performing it, and allows you to select a different order.
Tooltip.ruRU: Отменить текущий приказ и отдать следующий.

Tooltip.enUS: Drops the current order without performing it, and allows you to select a different order.
Tooltip.ruRU: Отменить текущий приказ и отдать следующий.

Tooltip.enUS: Drops the current order without performing it, and allows you to select a different order.
Tooltip.ruRU: Отменить текущий приказ и отдать следующий.

Tooltip.enUS: Cancels construction of this structure, destroying the structure and giving a partial refund.
Tooltip.ruRU: Отменить сооружение этого строения, уничтожив его и получив частичную компенсацию.

Tooltip.enUS: Selects the unit constructing this structure.
Tooltip.ruRU: Выбрать рабочего, который сооружает это строение.

Tooltip.zhCN:
莫比斯重型攻击机甲，攻击对地面单位造成小范围伤害。能够使用炮火覆盖对指定区域造成毁灭性打击。可以使用隐形、自我修复和战术折跃技能。

可以对地和对空。
Tooltip.enUS:
Mobius heavy attack mecha, its attack causes small-scale damage to ground units. Able to use artillery coverage to cause devastating damage to designated areas. Can use stealth, self-repair and tactical warp skills.

Can be used against ground and air.

Tooltip.zhCN:
莫比斯反机械近战单位。攻击能够造成小范围EMP。拥有增幅方阵。

可以对地。
Tooltip.enUS:
Moebius anti-mechanical melee unit. The attack can cause a small area EMP. Has an amplifying square array.

Can target the ground.

Tooltip.zhCN:
莫比斯近距离战斗机甲，对前方锥形区域造成范围伤害。可跃向敌方单位。能够变形为高速反轻甲战车。可以使用后燃推进、车体过载和引擎熔毁技能。

可以对地。
Tooltip.enUS:
Moebius is a close-range combat mecha that causes range damage to the cone area in front. Can jump to enemy units. Able to transform into a high-speed anti-light armor tank. Can use afterburning propulsion, hull overload and engine meltdown skills.

Can target the ground.

Tooltip.zhCN:
莫比斯重火力支援机甲，使用磁轨武器对一条直线上的地面单位造成范围伤害。能够翻越悬崖。

可以对地和对空。
Tooltip.enUS:
Moebius is a heavy fire support mecha that uses rail weapons to cause area damage to ground units in a straight line. Able to climb over cliffs.

Can be used against ground and air.

Name.zhCN: 折跃军团方阵战甲

Tooltip.zhCN:
坚固的莫比斯战斗机甲。能够使用风暴飞弹舱对目标造成额外伤害。拥有增幅方阵。可以使用防御姿态技能。

可以对地。
Tooltip.enUS:
The sturdy Moebius battle mecha. Ability to use Storm Missile Pods to deal extra damage to targets. Has an amplifying square array. Can use defensive stance skills.

Can target the ground.

Tooltip.zhCN: 使该建筑可以解锁更多莫比斯单位，并提升50%的充能速度。
Tooltip.enUS: Allows this building to unlock more Moebius units and increase charging speed by 50%.

Tooltip.zhCN: 使该建筑可以解锁高级莫比斯单位，并提升50%的充能速度。
Tooltip.enUS: Allows this building to unlock advanced Moebius units and increase charging speed by 50%.

Tooltip.zhCN: 使该建筑可以解锁最终莫比斯单位，并提升100%的充能速度。
Tooltip.enUS: Allows this building to unlock the final Moebius unit and increase charging speed by 100%.

Name.zhCN: 折跃军团超重型攻城坦克
Name.enUS: WarpLegion Super Heavy Siege Tank

Tooltip.zhCN:
莫比斯超重型火力支援单位。能够造成大量范围伤害。可切换至攻城模式来提升火力。

可以对地。
Tooltip.enUS:
Moebius super heavy fire support unit. Can cause a lot of area damage. You can switch to siege mode to increase your firepower.

Can target the ground.
